descriptionHtml:
A few people had asked me to post my character model, so allow me to introduce Sasja, my Nord Huntress. Regrettably, I deleted the immediately post-Helgen game save, but with -showracemenu and a few screenshots, you can replicate any settings you like.

To get this exact look, you\'d need:

- Neckros Female Beauty Faces
- Eyebrows Match Hair
- Detailed Lips

Also, I\'d like to give a shout-out to rendermax, as I used his \"Nora\" character as a starting point.
author: Rubedo
